'''约翰内斯·开普勒号自动运载飞船'''或'''自动运载飞船002'''('''ATV-002''')，是一辆[[欧洲空间局|欧洲空间局]]发射的无人值守[[貨運飛船|货物补给飞船]]。它是以德国天文学家[[约翰内斯·开普勒|约翰内斯·开普勒]]的名字命名的。<ref name=esa>{{cite web | url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/ATV/SEMGNHWX3RF_0.html | title=Second ATV named after Johannes Kepler | date=19 February 2009 | publisher=ESA | accessdate=16 July 2010 | archive-date=2012-03-30 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XNO8qi3?url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/ATV/SEMGNHWX3RF_0.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>飞船发射于2011年2月17日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://spaceflightnow.com/ariane/v200/110217launch/index.html|title=Europe dispatches Johannes Kepler to space station|date=February 17, 2011|accessdate=March 20, 2011|author=Stephen Clark|publisher=Spaceflight Now|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308083045/https://spaceflightnow.com/ariane/v200/110217launch/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，任务是提供[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]的推进剂、空气和干货物。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/station/structure/iss_manifest.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-06-21 |archive-date=2006-05-13 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20060513083153/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/station/structure/iss_manifest.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在运载重量超过7000kg的货物时，约翰内斯·开普勒号的总质量超过20000kg，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2011/02/ariane-mission-launch-atv-2-space-station/|title=Ariane 5 launches ATV-2 for journey to the ISS|author=Chris Gebhardt|publisher=NASAspaceflight.com|date=2011-02-15|accessdate=2011-03-20|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224170205/https://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2011/02/ariane-mission-launch-atv-2-space-station/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是由欧空局发射的有史以来的最大有效载荷。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.esa.int/esaCP/SEM5ZFY1LJG_index_0.html | title=Europe’s ATV space ferry ready for launch | date=3 February 2011 | publisher=ESA | accessdate=3 February 2011 | archive-date=2012-10-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021011511/http://www.esa.int/esaCP/SEM5ZFY1LJG_index_0.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>约翰内斯·开普勒号自动运载飞船是第二辆自动运载飞船，延续2008的儒勒·凡尔纳号的使命。

自动运载飞船上的很多储备被用于航天飞机任务[[STS-133|STS-133]]和国际空间站远征26。<ref name=nasatv>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/nasatv/ |title=NASA.gov/multimedia/nasatv/: ''per NASA Live TV broadcast'' |access-date=2011-06-21 |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129033655/https://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/nasatv/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2011年6月20日和国际空间站分离前，[[返回数据收集器|返回数据收集器]]被放上飞船。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.space-travel.com/reports/Unique_Aerospace_Invention_Ready_For_Debut_999.html|title=Unique Aerospace Invention Ready For Debut|accessdate=29 March 2011|date=29 March 2011|publisher=Space Travel.com|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817202439/http://www.space-travel.com/reports/Unique_Aerospace_Invention_Ready_For_Debut_999.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

